item.title: CVE-2020-4197|2024-08-04T08:00:06.951Z -- ibm -- tivoli%20netcool%2Fomnibus
item.description: IBM Tivoli Netcool/OMNIbus_GUI 8.1.0 allows web pages to be stored locally which can be read by another user on the system. IBM X-Force ID: 174908.

item.title: CVE-2020-4198|2024-08-04T08:00:06.880Z -- ibm -- tivoli%20netcool%2Fomnibus
item.description: IBM Tivoli Netcool/OMNIbus_GUI 8.1.0 is vulnerable to cross-site scripting. This vulnerability allows users to embed arbitrary JavaScript code in the Web UI thus altering the intended functionality potentially leading to credentials disclosure within a trusted session. IBM X-Force ID: 174909.

item.title: CVE-2020-4199|2024-08-04T08:00:07.091Z -- ibm -- tivoli%20netcool%2Fomnibus
item.description: IBM Tivoli Netcool/OMNIbus 8.1.0 is vulnerable to cross-site request forgery which could allow an attacker to execute malicious and unauthorized actions transmitted from a user that the website trusts. IBM X-Force ID: 174910.
